data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! Looking for the perfect starter home or to downsize then look no further, this adorable ranch home just right out of town is waiting for you! This home has 2 bedrooms, full bath, good size living area, kitchen and partially finished basement.  Outside there is a large fenced in yard and 2 car heated detached garage for all your toys. Call Lindsey Farrell 570.854.3849 for your private showing!
